    "index.013.welcome_to_clodia_intern": "Welcome to Clodia International FZE",
    "index.014.clodia_international_fze": "Clodia International FZE operates from Sharjah Airport Free Zone as the UAE trade and clearing subsidiary of International Finance Corporation, the Miami-based parent of our group. Within the group structure, our sister entity IFB Holdings LLC acts as the US buyer of record in commodity and metals transactions. Clodia handles what happens on the UAE side: customs, refining through DMCC Good Delivery accredited partners, secured vaulting, and the documentation chain that keeps every transaction auditable in both directions.",
    "index.015.the_separation_is_intent": "The separation is intentional. Sourcing and pricing gold is one discipline. Importing it into the UAE in compliance with the Ministry of Economy's 2024 due diligence regulations is another. Most cross-border gold deals fail at the second, not the first. Clodia exists to make sure they do not.",
