    "index.034.compliance_depth_uae_min": "<strong style=\"color:var(--white)\">Compliance depth.</strong> UAE Ministerial Decree 68 of 2024, OECD five-step guidance, DMCC Good Delivery rules, Dodd-Frank Section 1502 conflict minerals law, full sanctions screening across UN, EU, OFAC, and UAE lists. Every cargo carries its own audit file.",
    "index.035.delivery_record_saif_zon": "<strong style=\"color:var(--white)\">Delivery record.</strong> SAIF Zone location, partner refinery network, security carrier relationships, customs clearance infrastructure, assembled to deliver on the quoted date. Most of the time, they do.",
