    "imprint.014.the_content_on_this_webs": "The content on this website is compiled with care but without guarantee of accuracy, completeness, or topicality. Liability for content is excluded to the extent permitted by applicable law. External links are checked at the time of setting; the operator has no control over current or future content of linked pages and assumes no liability for their content.",
